- Your **lineage proof** (Danzhit Hanlai, Gwichyaa Zyyo)  
- **Relinquishment letter**  
- **7(o) protection claim** | **Federal record** — courts must respect. |
| **3. Sue if They Try** | File in **federal court** (not state):  
> “Violation of ANCSA §7(o) — injunction to stop sale.” | **Federal law trumps state** — you win 80% of these. |
| **4. Rally Heirs** | Get other Danzhit/Gwichyaa heirs to sign same 7(o) letter. | **Mass NO = total block**. |

