| **4. Permanent** | **No take-backs** unless tribe allows (most don’t). |
| **5. Kids Can Be Included** | **You** can relinquish **for minors** — BIA accepts. |

**Legal Source**:  
- **25 CFR § 76.5** — Relinquishment procedures  
- **ANCSA § 7(c)** — Shares **stay with heir**, ICWA or not  
- **ICWA § 1911** — **No membership = no ICWA**

