| **Field** | **Fill Like This** |
|---------|-------------------|
| **Applicant** | [Your Name], heir of Danzhit Hanlai |
| **Site Name** | “Danzhit Hanlai Burial Ground” |
| **Location** | Sec 12, T10N, R15E, Fairbanks Meridian |
| **Acreage** | 40 acres |
| **Use** | Cemetery + sacred trail |
| **Title To** | Gwichyaa Zyyo Village Corporation |

