ANCSA's **Section 14(h)(1)** has protected over **1.1 million acres** of sacred sites since 1971 — graves, villages, trails, and camps that **can't be sold or developed**. Here are **4 real success stories** from Alaska Natives who've used it to win big. These aren't hypotheticals; they're documented cases from BIA records and Native corps.

