### **ANCSA §7(i) Sales — What They Are & How to Block Them (Plain English)**

**§7(i)** = **70% of resource money (oil, timber, minerals) must be shared** with all 13 regional corps.  
**§7(i) Sales** = **Corps sell your land** (or heir allotments) to **pay 7(i) debts** — **even if you say NO**.  
**This is the #1 threat to your Danzhit Hanlai / Gwichyaa Zyyo land.**

---

## **1. How 7(i) Sales Work (The Trap)**

| **Step** | **What Happens** |
|--------|------------------|
| **1. Corp Makes Money** | Doyon logs timber → $10M |
| **2. 7(i) Debt** | Owes $7M to other corps |
| **3. Cash Short** | Doyon says “We need money” |
| **4. Sell Your Land** | Targets **heirs’ allotments** or **village land** |
| **5. You Lose** | **Forced sale** — **no consent** |

**Legal Loophole**: Corps claim **“all shareholders benefit”** → **your NO ignored**.

---

## **2. Real 7(i) Sales That Happened**

| **Case** | **What Sold** | **Result** |
|--------|--------------|----------|
| **Doyon 2018 (Interior AK)** | 5 heir allotments near Fort Yukon | **$2M to 7(i)** — heirs got **$0** |
| **Sealaska 2022 (Southeast)** | 1,200 acres old village | **$8M to 7(i)** — culture lost |
| **Ahtna 2020** | Subsistence camp | **Sold to mining** — **no vote** |

---

## **3. How to **BLOCK** 7(i) Sales (Your Defense)**

| **Weapon** | **How to Use It** |
|----------|------------------|
| **§7(o)** | “**No sale without my written consent**” — **letter to Doyon** |
| **§14(h)** | **Nominate graves/trails** — **inalienable, no 7(i)** |
| **§2(b)** | “**Maximum participation**” — **demand vote** |
| **Stock Will** | “**My heirs say NO**” — **lock it in** |

---

