### **ANCSA §14(h) Protections — Your Sacred Land Shield (Plain English)**

**§14(h)** = **Congress’s promise**:  
> **“Graves, old villages, trails, and sacred sites are **inalienable** — **no sale, no lease, no 7(i), no roads, no mining — ever.**”**

This is **your strongest lock** — **stronger than 7(o), stronger than 2(b)**.  
**Once nominated and approved, it’s **bulletproof**._

---

