| **Site** | **Protected From** | **Forever?** |
|--------|-------------------|------------|
| **Cemeteries** | Sale, mining, roads | **YES** |
| **Old Villages** | 7(i) timber, battery pads | **YES** |
| **Trails** | Yukon/Ambler access | **YES** |
| **Sacred Spots** | Any development | **YES** |

**Total Protected**: **~1.1 million acres** across Alaska.

